      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a bit sad to see this absolute beauty go. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, kept tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and pampered like one of the family. It drives like a dream and looks just as sharp as the day it rolled off the lot. You might find a microscopic speck if you really hunt for it, but for all intents and purposes, she\u2019s a total gem. I\u2019m looking for someone who will love it as much as I have. Come take a look and let's get you behind the wheel!",
